          "slidetitle": "Unintended Consequences of AI Bloat",
          "subtitle": "When more AI means more problems.",
          "slidecontent": "• Overlapping AI features that conflict with each other, confusing users and breaking workflows\n• Slower performance\n• Each added model increases the attack surface for security vulnerabilities\n• Harder to debug when something goes wrong\n• Users lose trust quickly when AI behaves unpredictably across different parts of a product\n• More AI, more liability"
